                                <h4 class="uppercase main-color" style="line-height: 22px;">Fees: Behind the-Wheel Training Program</h4>
                                <h5 style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 25px; margin-top: 10px"> 6 Hours Lessons + Car fee for Road test --> $320.00 <br> 8 Hours Lessons + Car fee for Road test --> $400.00 <br> 10 Hours Lessons + Car fee for Road test --> $460.00 <br> 2 Hours Practice + Car fee for Road test --> $200.00 </h5>
